The paper discusses the application of the interactive-predictive framework to multimodal neural sequence to sequence models for image and video captioning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves computer vision and machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with multimodal problems, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.MM (Multimedia).
